630
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,030
Tidak perlu ada laki-laki di rumah.

631
00:31:42,030 --> 00:31:43,790
Bukankah Anda setuju, Yang Mulia?

632
00:31:45,270 --> 00:31:46,200
Penggemar,

633
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:48,550
